              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "FRS"
                ],
                "institute": "2GERGSI"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The velocity filter SHIP(Separator for",
                " Heavy-Ion reaction Products) at GSI."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The evaporated residues(ERs) were",
                "separated from the beam by the velocity filter SHIP and",
                "implanted into a position-sensitive strip Si detector",
                " (focal-plane stop detector)"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The detector system was completed by a Si veto detector",
                "and a Ge clover detector, both mounted behind the",
                "stop detector. The clover detector was separated from",
                "the SHIP vacuum by a 1mm thick aluminium window."
              ]
            }
          ],
